                            <comment id="14467685" author="hermit69" created="Mon, 14 Sep 2009 07:18:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve got some more details on this bug. Say that &quot;This is &lt;/p&gt;
{@code xxx}
&lt;p&gt;&quot; is the first sentenceof a method comment.&lt;br/&gt;
Then in the summary where it only displays the first sentence it will display &quot;This is {&quot;. However, in the method&lt;br/&gt;
details section it will display it correctly. Obviously it thinks that &quot;{&quot; ends a sentence when, of course, it doesn&apos;t.&lt;br/&gt;
Hope this helps.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Steve&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
